ll}, {"url": "https://www.mining-technology.com/news/us-steel-nippon-steel-merger", "title": "US Steel, Nippon Steel merger gains nod of non-US regulators", "content": "US Steel president and CEO David Burritt said: \\u201cWe are pleased with the regulatory approvals received, as they are a clear indication that the transaction with Nippon Steel is pro-competitive and supports the strategic merits of foreign investment.\\n\\n\\u201cTogether with Nippon Steel, US Steel will become a world-leading steelmaker with enhanced technologies and resources to support a stronger steel industry with enhanced competition.", "score": 0.5923135, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://gmk.center/en/news/biden-plans-to-block-the-merger-of-nippon-steel-and-us-steel-bloomberg", "title": "Biden plans to block the merger of Nippon Steel and US Steel - Bloomberg", "content": "Tags:\\n\\nUS, Nippon Steel, US Steel, sale\\n\\n Photo \\u2013 Biden plans to block the merger of Nippon Steel and US Steel \\u2013 Bloomberg\\n\\n  Mauro Longobardo  \\n  Chief Executive Officer at ArcelorMittal Kryvyi Rih\\n\\n  Opinions Industry CBAM\\n\\n  11 June 2026\\n\\n  Ukrainian steel sector has withstood war, but now it needs Europe\\u2019s fairness\\n\\n  CBAM and steel import quotas were designed to protect European producers, but now they risk hurting a future EU member\\u2019s industrial backbone\\n\\nRelated Articles", "score": 0.5769478, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://journal-neo.su/2024/10/10/on-the-political-issues-and-problems-related-to-the-planned-merger-between-nippon-steel-and-us-steel", "title": "Merger of Nippon Steel and US Steel: an important event for the industry", "content": "Last August, the management of US Steel Corporation (USS), one of America\\u2019s oldest companies, said it was looking for a \\u201cstrategic investor\\u201d to resolve years of accumulated problems. Of all the contenders, by December 2023, Japan\\u2019s Nippon Steel (NS) Corporation had emerged as the 