uthority.", "score": 0.6147415, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://www.pymnts.com/cpi-posts/us-steel-and-nippon-steel-secure-international-approvals-for-14-9b-merger", "title": "US Steel and Nippon Steel Secure International Approvals for $14.9B Merger", "content": "The U.S. Department of Justice is rigorously examining the proposed transaction. In response to the mounting concerns, Nippon Steel has pledged to honor all existing agreements between U.S. Steel and the union. Additionally, Nippon Steel has committed to relocating its U.S. headquarters to Pittsburgh, where U.S. Steel is currently based, in a bid to alleviate some of the apprehensions surrounding the merger.", "score": 0.57437146, "raw_content": null}]',
